      About this item

      • IMMERSIVE LAB QUALITY SOUND: Enjoy exceptional sound quality via 40mm drivers, bringing depth and clarity to your music. With 70+ hours of playtime (40+ hours with ANC on), enjoy uninterrupted music sessions or calls. Enjoy another dimension and immersive sound with Spatial Audio, compatible with applications such as Dolby Atmos, Tempest 3D AudioTech and Windows Sonic. Youll feel like youre sitting in the middle of a concert or standing in the middle of a fight scene.
      • SMART ANC AND BE AWARE MODE: Smart Active Noise Cancelation adjusts to the environment and continually learns how to best cancel noises, offering the best audio experience. Activate the Smart Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 35 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment.
      • CLOUD FOAM COMFORT: Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.
      • CUSTOMIZE YOUR SOUND + EXPERIENCE VIA JLAB APP: With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available.
      • CRYSTAL CLEAR CALLS: Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.
      • EASY CONNECTIONS + GOOGLE FIND MY: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair. Plus with Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones.
      • FOLDABLE DESIGN WITH ROTATING EARCUPS: Designed for convenience and portability, these headphones are easy to store and carry.
      • SPATIAL AUDIO COMPATIBLE

          1. IMMERSIVE LAB QUALITY SOUND


            With 70+ hours of playtime (40+ hours with ANC on), enjoy uninterrupted music sessions or calls. Enjoy another dimension and immersive sound with Spatial Audio, compatible with applications such as Dolby Atmos, Tempest 3D AudioTech and Windows Sonic. Youll feel like youre sitting in the middle of a concert or standing in the middle of a fight scene.

          2. CLOUD FOAM COMFORT


            Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.

          3. CUSTOMIZE YOUR SOUND + EXPERIENCE VIA JLAB APP


            With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available.

          4. CRYSTAL CLEAR CALLS


            Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.

          5. EASY CONNECTIONS + GOOGLE FIND MY


            Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones.

          How customer reviews and ratings work

          Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

          To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

          Amazon Customer
          5 out of 5 stars
          Fantastic ANC Headphones!
          I was looking for a pair of noise canceling headphones to help me with my sensory issues. Ive tried different kinds of earbuds (loops, flares, etc.) and cant stand the feeling of them for long. When it came to headphones Im much more used to the feeling of pressure and heat while wearing them as I do a lot of gaming, and I wanted to avoid that for daily use. Comfort: These have none of the above issues I mentioned, theres no pressure on my head, no heat or discomfort. Theyre extremely lightweight and adjustable. I have large gauges in my ears (7/8) though I do have small ears, and they still fit perfectly and comfortably and dont pinch me at all at the bottom. The design allows them to fold up small enough to be easily held in one hand (and I have very small hands) or put inside of a purse or bag for travel. The ANC settings: As an autistic individual I wanted these headphones purely for this purpose, and it works FANTASTICALLY. I turned on the ANC and could no longer hear the electricity and fridge running in my house, it muffled outside sounds so well it was actually almost uncomfortable, it gave a sensation of cotton in the ears for me. The next setting was be aware mode, and it also works fabulously. This setting seems to listen to surroundings and amplify it through the speakers so you can better hear whats going on around you, even while listening to music, similar to microphone playback or pass through on gaming headsets. The last setting in ANC modes is ANC off, this setting feels and sounds like a normal pair of headphones, just enough muffling to be comfortable and still hear things but just dampens it slightly. Movie/Music modes: These headphones also have movie mode and music mode, theres not a huge difference between the two but I found when using movie mode to watch videos it sounds more similar to being in a room with the person speaking, so theres much more clarity to me. Jlab App: I found the app to work perfectly for me, as soon as I opened it with Bluetooth connected it found the device immediately, and then started an update. There is preset EQ versions, and a fully customizable EQ board. You are also able to fully customize the button settings from the app. My favorite aspect of the app is that it has built in ambient sounds that you can layer and customize such as rain, birds, space, and frequency music. I found the sounds to be very relaxing and actually well done, often times ambient sounds, like birds, can be too sharp which just adds to sensory overload for me; these are more soft and clear sounds. You can even adjust the individual volumes for each sound. The music quality is great even on basic EQ settings, its not mind blowing by any means but theres nothing I would complain about. And the built in microphone seems to work very well on phone calls, I was told I sounded clearer than I normally do over my iPhone 11. I genuinely dont understand how this headset could have such negative reviews unless they either got a bad set or didnt use the app to update their headphones. UPDATE YOUR HEADPHONES with the app BEFORE you test everything out. I noticed a difference in sound quality after updating. I only wish these came in more punchy colors like hot pink or lilac, other than that, theyre perfect and worth every penny. Ive shared them with a couple family members who will be ordering their own sets as well.

          • IMMERSIVE LAB QUALITY SOUND: Enjoy exceptional sound quality via 40mm drivers, bringing depth and clarity to your music. With 70+ hours of playtime (40+ hours with ANC on), enjoy uninterrupted music sessions or calls. Enjoy another dimension and immersive sound with Spatial Audio, compatible with applications such as Dolby Atmos, Tempest 3D AudioTech and Windows Sonic. Youll feel like youre sitting in the middle of a concert or standing in the middle of a fight scene.
          • SMART ANC AND BE AWARE MODE: Smart Active Noise Cancelation adjusts to the environment and continually learns how to best cancel noises, offering the best audio experience. Activate the Smart Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 35 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment.
          • CLOUD FOAM COMFORT: Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.
          • CUSTOMIZE YOUR SOUND + EXPERIENCE VIA JLAB APP: With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available.
          • CRYSTAL CLEAR CALLS: Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.
          • EASY CONNECTIONS + GOOGLE FIND MY: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair. Plus with Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones.
          • FOLDABLE DESIGN WITH ROTATING EARCUPS: Designed for convenience and portability, these headphones are easy to store and carry.
          • SPATIAL AUDIO COMPATIBLE

          Product Description

          UNFORGETTABLE SOUND. UNPARALLELED LUXURY. Experience luxurious sound with JBuds Lux ANC Headphonesa new legacy in JLab audio excellence. Seamlessly blending innovation and Lab-quality sound, these sleek headphones guarantee an elevated listening experience. Whether in a bustling commute or unwinding, revel in uninterrupted music bliss with Hybrid Active Noise Canceling and personalized sound via the JLab App. Embrace your favorite tunes or podcasts in ultimate comfort and style with Cloud Foam earcups and headband, ensuring an unparalleled listening experience. IMMERSIVE LAB QUALITY SOUND Enjoy exceptional sound quality via 40mm drivers, bringing depth and clarity to your music. With 70+ hours of playtime (40+ hours with ANC on), enjoy uninterrupted music sessions or calls. Enjoy another dimension and immersive sound with Spatial Audio, compatible with applications such as Dolby Atmos, Tempest 3D AudioTech and Windows Sonic. Youll feel like youre sitting in the middle of a concert or standing in the middle of a fight scene. HYBRID ANC AND BE AWARE MODE Hybrid Active Noise Cancelation adjusts to the environment and continually learns how to best cancel noises, offering the best audio experience. Activate the Hybrid Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 35 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment. CLOUD FOAM COMFORT Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute. CUSTOMIZE YOUR SOUND + EXPERIENCE VIA JLAB APP With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available. Available on the Google Play Store or Apple. CRYSTAL CLEAR CALLS Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience. EASY CONNECTIONS + GOOGLE FIND MY Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair. When you take out your headphones and have a supported Android device, youll see a pop-up enabling you to connect via Bluetooth. Dont worry if youre not an Android user, JLab headphones will connect with any Bluetooth enabled device like iPhone with just a couple taps. Plus with Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones.
